results.name: Decimal expansion of c/P in SI units (meters), where c is the speed of light in vacuum and P is the number of periods of the radiation corresponding to the transition between the two hyperfine levels of the ground state of the caesium 133 atom in one second.
results.author: _Omar E. Pol_, Jul 06 2014
